audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design\V1.14_PLAN_AND_DECISIONS.md:21:- Not a fixed multiplier. The object is Δ as a **surface governed by the credit-versus-coverage mechanism.**
audits/2026-07-11-v1.14-design\V1.14_PLAN_AND_DECISIONS.md:24:  boundary — not a multiplier — is the object that requires measurement."*  A falsifiable comparative-institutions
